file.name: order.openapi.yaml
file.content:
---
openapi: 3.0.1
info:
  title: FavFood Integration API
  version: "1.0"
paths:
  /api/order:
    get:
      responses:
        "200":
          description: OK
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/Order'
components:
  schemas:
    LineItem:
      type: object
      properties:
        item:
          type: string
        itemId:
          type: string
        quantity:
          format: int32
          type: integer
    ListLineItem:
      type: array
      items:
        $ref: '#/components/schemas/LineItem'
    Order:
      type: object
      properties:
        customerName:
          type: string
        id:
          type: string
        lineItems:
          $ref: '#/components/schemas/ListLineItem'
